{"tid":729973,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英撚發現英格蘭奪冠方程式","createTime":"2018-07-05T04:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T13:38:57.000Z","uid":8246,"like":70,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"921166db1470a4e8fabd09715ec256fefe907d09","tid":729973,"uid":8246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:27:22.000Z","msg":"66年皇馬奪歐聯冠軍、曼城捧聯賽冠軍(當時乙組)、車路士聯賽排第5位、般尼取得歐洲賽資格，今年全部都應驗晒！<br />\n英格蘭對上一次世界盃成績好過德國，就係1966年<br />\n<br />\n30(66年決賽日期) x 4(英格蘭決賽入波) =120<br />\n120 / 2(德國決賽入波) = 60<br />\n60 - 8(第8屆世界盃) = 52<br />\n52 + 1966(英格蘭奪冠年份) = 2018<br />\n<br />\n所以今年到英格蘭了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e42f975bf28c0ff2ad0f32415fcdf74566fce2b","tid":729973,"uid":8246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cccc2a24a40ef7acdee8b39d538f97e9c5715e85","tid":729973,"uid":31314,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:37:01.000Z","msg":"2014+4=2018<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5702bcda5fa9636eff7cde9ef37dc8fe470fc816","tid":729973,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:40:31.000Z","msg":"掂啦今次"},{"pid":"1beec4f3836368c8d4fefa03c4a0fbb58bf3caf0","tid":729973,"uid":183302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"Ok all in英撚  16號準時睇約睇樓"},{"pid":"7eaf8460ab4b571a0c178b668fbdb20cb567b5e6","tid":729973,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1beec4f3836368c8d4fefa03c4a0fbb58bf3caf0","tid":729973,"uid":183302,